Text: MS AwardsWeve never met but as a long time geophysical consultant to EOG and now EGEP I thought Id send a congratulatory note from a fellow MS rider on your top fundraising achievement announced last night at the Awards evening Its good to know that theres time to ride in what must be a very busy schedule Best regards Mike Yates mailto Visualization Center Manager Continuum Resources International Corp Old Katy Road Suite Houston Tx Direct Main Fax
